<ol>
  <li>The financial cost of decanting the estate including buy-out costs of leaseholders.</li>
  <li>The loss of rental income for the Council both in the short term and long term.</li>
  <li>The social cost of decants on the housing waiting list and temporary accommodation costs.</li>
  <li>The environmental cost of discarding thousands of tonnes of embodied carbon and generating thousands of tonnes of new uneccessary carbon emissions in the new-build construction.</li>
</ol>

